<br>
War is the essence of Norrath. We wage war from the moment we are brought into this world, the moment our training is complete. We fight constantly. With out battle, war or conflict, Norrath would be nothing. Our Gods wage war against one another as they have for hundreds of thousands of years. <br>
<br>
War is not Evil, War is life. War, battle and fighting bring each and every one of us a life that we can live.<br>
<br>
