You are correct. But conflict is what drives us and that leads to war. My people are in a constant war with the halflings at the moment. The Trolls are at war with the Frogloks. Internal wars rage in every human city. The Fier'Dal and Koada'Dal wage a never ending war agianst the orcs of Crush Bone, albeit that the orcs have the aid of my kind. The Gnomes fight against the minotars and kobolds. Dwarves wage a constant battle against the goblins. Halflings, those who preach of peace, fight constantly against the goblins of Runny Eye. In fact, only my limited knowledge of the Vah Shir keep me from pointing out the war they rage. You Iksar claim to be the rulers of Kunark, that it is your birth right. <br>
<br>
Norrath belongs to those who are strong enough to take it from others. Only those who wield the fire and sword will some day come to rule this world. <br>
